Packages 
Package Description
meico
Contains all sub-packages and classes that form meico.
meico.audio
Meico's audio data related classes.
meico.mei
Contains the MEI class and a Helper class that is mostly used for MEI processing but offers some useful functionality also for other datatypes such as MSM and MPM.
meico.midi
Classes and tools for representing and processing MIDI data.
meico.mpm
This package holds the official Music Performance Markup API.
meico.mpm.elements
Contains the classes for all MPM elements.
meico.mpm.elements.maps
Contains the classes for MPM maps.
meico.mpm.elements.maps.data
The classes in this package represent performance data.
meico.mpm.elements.metadata
Classes to interface MPM metadata.
meico.mpm.elements.styles
Contains classes to interface MPM style collections and style definitions.
meico.mpm.elements.styles.defs
Classes that represent entries in an MPM style definition.
meico.msm
Contains classes to handle Musical Sequence Markup data.
meico.musicxml
Contains classes to interface MusicXML data.
meico.pitches
Contains classes for musical pitch information, e.g.
meico.supplementary
Some data structures and functionality that is useful across the different data types.
meico.svg
Classes to handle SVG (Scalable Vector Graphics) data.
meico.xml
Contains classes to handle XML data.
